{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/hungry-hearts-diner-tale-star-crossed-souls-game-kombinasi-game-restaurant-dengan-cerita-yang-menyentuh/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Hungry Hearts Diner: A Tale of Star-Crossed Souls Game, Kombinasi Game Restaurant dengan Cerita yang Menyentuh.","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sebuah game yang memiliki gameplay bagus itu biasa. Tapi kalau game bagus disertai dengan cerita yang menyentuh, itu baru luar biasa! Hungry Hearts Diner: A Tale of Star-Crossed Souls adalah game yang mengambil lokasi di sebuah restaurant kecil di tengah kota Jepang.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dengan desain konsep kedai tradisional, bro sis akan berperan sebagai seorang nenek tua, sang pemilik restaurant. Sembari menjalankan restaurantnya, Sang nenek juga harus menemani dan merawat suaminya yang sedang sakit.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_32786\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-32786\" data-attachment-id=\"32786\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/hungry-hearts-diner-tale-star-crossed-souls-game-kombinasi-game-restaurant-dengan-cerita-yang-menyentuh/attachment/6-146/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/6-20.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Hungry Hearts Diner\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Hungry Hearts Diner&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/6-20.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/6-20.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-32786 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/6-20.jpg\" alt=\"Hungry Hearts Diner upgrade\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-32786\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Hungry Hearts Diner</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/5-mmorpg-mobile-baru-yang-patut-kamu-tunggu-di-2018/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">5 MMORPG Mobile Baru Yang Patut Kamu Tunggu di 2018!</a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sama halnya seperti game restaurant lainnya, bro sis diharusnya untuk melayani customer yang datang ke restaurant. Setelah itu, customer akan memberikan uang yang nantinya bisa dipakai untuk membeli kebutuhan restaurant seperti meja, kursi, dan lain-lain. Ditemani oleh <em>background</em> musik yang menenangkan serta desain restaurant yang <em>vintage</em>, dijamin bro sis bakal ketagihan untuk terus memainkan game ini! (Seriusan background musiknya enak banget!)</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_32789\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-32789\" data-attachment-id=\"32789\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/hungry-hearts-diner-tale-star-crossed-souls-game-kombinasi-game-restaurant-dengan-cerita-yang-menyentuh/attachment/7-118/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/7-16.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Hungry Hearts Diner\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Hungry Hearts Diner&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/7-16.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/7-16.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-32789 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/7-16.jpg\" alt=\"Hungry Hearts Diner gameplay\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-32789\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Hungry Hearts Diner</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nah, yang membedakan game ini dengan jenis game restaurant lainnya, adalah ceritanya. Setiap customer yang datang mempunyai cerita, masalah dan kisah hidup masing-masing. Untuk memancing customer untuk bercerita, bro sis harus memasak makanan kesukaan masing-masing customer. Inilah inti dari game ini, tak hanya memasak, customer dari game ini juga memiliki cerita yang hangat dan menyentuh untuk didengar.</p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"32774\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/hungry-hearts-diner-tale-star-crossed-souls-game-kombinasi-game-restaurant-dengan-cerita-yang-menyentuh/attachment/2-157/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/2-25.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/2-25.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/2-25.jpg\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-32774 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/2-25.jpg\" alt=\"Hungry hearts Diner menu\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-florence-kisah-cinta-interaktif-dalam-perangkat-mobile-yang-inovatif/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Game Florence, Kisah Cinta Interaktif dalam Perangkat Mobile yang Inovatif</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Good food and Good Story in Hungry Hearts Diner</strong></h2>\n<blockquote><p>What makes people more talkative than a full belly?</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Semakin banyak kita memasak, maka akan semakin banyak pula menu baru yang akan muncul. Kita juga bisa mengetahui berbagai menu masakan Jepang mulai dari masakan nasi, lauk, <em>side dish</em> dan <em>dessert</em>! Berbagai masakan Jepang dari yang tradisional sampai modern juga ada di Hungry Hearts Diner. Hmm, bikin laper puol deh pokoknya!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_32777\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-32777\" data-attachment-id=\"32777\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/hungry-hearts-diner-tale-star-crossed-souls-game-kombinasi-game-restaurant-dengan-cerita-yang-menyentuh/attachment/3-182/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/3-25.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"what makes people more talkative than a full belly?\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;what makes people more talkative than a full belly?&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/3-25.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/3-25.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-32777 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/3-25.jpg\" alt=\"Hungry hearts Diner dialogue\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-32777\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">what makes people more talkative than a full belly?</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cerita masing-masing customer tentunya tidak semua yang berakhir bahagia, ada yang menyentuh, bahagia maupun yang menyakitkan. Namun semuanya mempunyai hikmah yang bisa diambil. Bisa dibilang, sejauh ini, game Hungry Hearts Diner merupakan game yang paling menyentuh yang pernah penulis mainkan. Ditambah dengan musiknya! Yes, sekali lagi, <em>background</em> musiknya nenangin banget.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_32771\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-32771\" data-attachment-id=\"32771\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/hungry-hearts-diner-tale-star-crossed-souls-game-kombinasi-game-restaurant-dengan-cerita-yang-menyentuh/attachment/1-215/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/1-29.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Hungry Hearts Diner\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Hungry Hearts Diner&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/1-29.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/1-29.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-32771 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/1-29.jpg\" alt=\"Hungry hearts Diner wish\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-32771\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Hungry Hearts Diner</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tidak seperti game restaurant atau <em>cooking</em> yang fokus pada level, game ini mempunyai cerita dan ending yang menyentuh. Apabila customer kepuasannya sudah mencapai 100 persen. Kita akan mengetahui kisah Sang nenek yang juga mempunyai endingnya sendiri. Dan seriusan deh, pasti bakalan buat kamu bingung, ga nyangka, sedih, senang, terharu, pokoknya nano nano deh!</p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"32783\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/hungry-hearts-diner-tale-star-crossed-souls-game-kombinasi-game-restaurant-dengan-cerita-yang-menyentuh/attachment/5-179/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/5-25.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"5\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/5-25.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/5-25.jpg\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-32783 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/5-25.jpg\" alt=\"Hungry hearts Diner customer\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Hungry Hearts Diner is really worth to be played. I love love love the story! Thank you for such a beautiful, heartwarming game!</em> Bagi bro sis yang tertarik dengan game ini, bisa langsung melipir ke playstore dan appstore gadget kamu!</p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"32780\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/hungry-hearts-diner-tale-star-crossed-souls-game-kombinasi-game-restaurant-dengan-cerita-yang-menyentuh/attachment/4-173/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/4-24.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"4\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/4-24.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/4-24.jpg\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-32780 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/4-24.jpg\" alt=\"Hungry hearts Diner customer 2\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"bc9becd8-32e5-5ceb-a4cd-ac472a5728c2"}}}